
# Pocket FT8 Libraries
- AGUI:  Another Graphical User Interface provides a highly curated set of GUI controls for embedded systems constructed over Adafruit's GFX Library in the Arduino framework.
- ft8:  A port of kgoba's ft8_lib into the Pocket FT8 code project with a few Pocket FT8 dependencies. 
- GPShelper:  Very small collection of helper functions constructed over Adafruit's GPS library with Pocket FT8 hardware dependencies.
- HX8357_t3n:  A port of the mjs513 driver for the Adafruit HX8357D 3.5" TFT display.
- lexical:  A tiny library of helper functions for character strings.
- locator:  Small library of Maidenhead grid square functions.
- locator:  QSO logging classes for ADIF and CSV.
- radix64:  Simple radix64 conversions.
- si5351:  A port of the github etherkit Si5351Arduino library with support for multiple I2C busses.
- timer:  A simple Timer class for the Arduino framework
- TinySet:  A simple Set class
- TouchScreen:  A touchscreen library providing calibration, display screen coordinates and many enhancements
- UserInterface:  The Pocket FT8 user interface class implemented as a library only to make it available to Unity tests